Additionally, the paper deals with holography, which could fall under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. The use of generative adversarial networks (GANs) also suggests that the paper could belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The paper also involves the reconstruction of 3D images, which could fall under the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category. Finally, the paper involves the use of wave propagation, which could fall under the information theory (cs.IT) sub-category.
